Trembling Before G-d;;74;;89;;NC;;"Trembling Before G-d" is an unprecedented feature documentary that shatters assumptions about faith, sexuality, and religious fundamentalism. Built around intimately-told personal stories of Hasidic and Orthodox Jews who are gay or lesbian, the film portrays a group of people who face a profound dilemma -- how to reconcile their passionate love of Judaism and the Divine with the drastic Biblical prohibitions that forbid homosexuality.;;Documentary;;Sandi Simcha DuBowski;;2001;;NC;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/trembling-before-gd